dct_description_sm: This point shapefile provides the locations of commercial biodiesel production plants in the United States for 2015. This layer is a part of a collection of GIS data containing renewable and electric energy information for the U.S., including data on transmission lines, power plants and electricity substations.
This layer can be used for locating and analysing existing commercial biodiesel production plants in the United States.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
